Package InfrastructureManager

Class PlatformObject

java.lang.Object
InfrastructureManager.PlatformObject
Direct Known Subclasses:
AdvantEdgeModuleObject, ConsoleModuleObject, MatchMakingModuleObject, ModuleDebugInput, NetworkModuleObject, RemoteExecutionModuleObject, RESTModuleObject, Runner, ScenarioModuleObject, UtilityModuleObject
public abstract class PlatformObject
extends java.lang.Object
Base class for objects of the platform. All modules should have a specific implementation that must extend this class. In turn, all objects on the module should extend it, in order to have access to its module's ModuleDebugInput and be able to log information. It also provides access to the ownerModule of each object, using its ImmutablePlatformModule interface,
